{"tid":1760750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「五大訴求、缺一不可」","createTime":"2019-11-28T12:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T16:23:11.000Z","uid":45123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aabbec0f35436679999db5166ca70aeebcc6be50","tid":1760750,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:21:49.000Z","msg":"不知道大家多少時間沒有說過這句?<br />\n雖然我們於不同的副線有所得著，<br />\n我們現時只達成一個訴求。<br />\n大家都忘記了其中一個訴求是真普選嗎？<br />\n然後大家就討論２０２０怎樣於立會選舉？<br />\n<br />\n「解散警隊、刻不容緩」<br />\n黑警對市民的債一點都沒有還。<br />\n７２１<br />\n８３１<br />\n多宗強姦案<br />\n多宗被自殺案<br />\n多宗警署內酷刑<br />\n被黑警打爆頭、斷手、斷腳的案件<br />\n催淚彈<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n一點都沒有還。<br />\n<br />\n還可以開這麼麼耐的香檳慶祝嗎？"},{"pid":"70c6f1c1ad029c4aea6b029bd66ceac5cfacd2b4","tid":1760750,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d289f0a6a46dd87a15a55edb2af75f84325f13af","tid":1760750,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"記起那些手足"},{"pid":"8b9ef8c824f6a9de3360bf75e68d3bb09f67906a","tid":1760750,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:26:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa071018a48f8799b4c8a63b383b2c0a62659560","tid":1760750,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"211d646be1b70500ee27828e7a1c43cffdeeea86","tid":1760750,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:28:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6db58a421f3c8ede49cdc6b9562659d7e5717f0f","tid":1760750,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59c932628f720e7a4c5ade2918e60da86355bf5","tid":1760750,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"